{"title":"通车那天","authors":["左新国"],"dates":[{"year":1990,"month":11,"day":30}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"通车那天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"左新国"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"通车那天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们将那顶风化的草帽"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抛向空中"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扯开嗓门高喊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"通——车——啰"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山谷回音河流回音"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"久久撞击心灵壁"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"通车那天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"城市乡村紧握久别的双手"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"嫣然一笑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"于是"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"许许多多陈腐偏见"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"被这一笑抖落"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"被这一笑抛出九霄云外"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"瞧，山村蹒跚的步伐变快啦"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一眨眼就是几十公里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"通车那天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们这个部落"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"唯一的信箱超载了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一只只洁白的鸽子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"穿过阳光的雨层"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飞向远方恋人母亲温馨的怀里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那天，我们这群筑路汉哟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"悄悄在地图册上涂一条红线"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（红线凝聚多少沉重岁月呀）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"悄悄将那页难忘的日子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"珍藏心底"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"通车那天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那列客车开动了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那列客车按铁路时刻表开动了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那列客车沿筑路者血脉运行了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"于是"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国少了一份拥挤"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"世界少了一份拥挤"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"欢庆的美酒令人陶醉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"通车那天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们这个小小的部落"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"真的被灌醉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在月光下山风中摇晃几下"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"便恬然睡去、睡去……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（作者单位：江西景德镇市铁道部四局五处）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}